---
export const prerender = true;
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for xConvert24. Learn how we handle data, cookies, and analytics. Your conversions stay in your browser." keywords="privacy policy, data protection, xConvert24 privacy, cookies, GDPR, user data">
  <div class="max-w-3xl prose dark:prose-invert prose-gray">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: June 2025</p>

    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      At xConvert24.com, your privacy matters to us. This policy explains what data we collect, why we collect it, and how you can manage it.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mt-4 mb-2">Automatically collected</h3>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
      <li>Page views and basic usage analytics (via Google Analytics)</li>
      <li>Approximate geographic location (country/region level)</li>
      <li>Device type, browser, and operating system</li>
      <li>Referral source (how you found us)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mt-4 mb-2">Stored locally on your device</h3>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
      <li>Theme preference (dark/light mode)</li>
      <li>Bookmarked pages</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">
      This data is stored in your browser's localStorage and is never transmitted to our servers.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 mt-4 mb-2">We do NOT collect</h3>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
      <li>Personal identification (name, email, phone)</li>
      <li>Conversion inputs or results</li>
      <li>Financial or health data</li>
      <li>Any data requiring an account (we have no accounts)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">2. How We Use Data</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Analytics data helps us understand which converters are popular, identify performance issues, and improve the user experience. We do not sell, rent, or share your data with third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">3. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
      <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — collects anonymised usage data. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — hosts and delivers our website. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Cloudflare's Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">4. Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      We use minimal cookies. See our <a href="/cookies" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a> for full details.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">You have the right to:</p>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
      <li>Clear your localStorage data at any time (browser settings → clear site data)</li>
      <li>Opt out of Google Analytics using the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">GA opt-out browser add-on</a></li>
      <li>Contact us to request information about any data we may hold</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">6. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Our service is available to all ages. We do not knowingly collect personal information from anyone, including children under 13.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-3">8. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">If you have questions about this privacy policy, please visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 hover:underline">contact page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
